FX.name: Air
FX.description: This effect reproduces the ambience of a room, to create spatial depth.

Parameters.name: Size
Parameters.explanation: Sets the size of the space.

Parameters.name: REF
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the amount of reflection from the wall.

Parameters.name: Mix
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the amount of effected sound that is mixed with the original sound.

Parameters.name: Tail
Parameters.explanation: When ON, effect sound continues even after effect is turned off. When OFF, effect sound stops right when effect is turned off.
